data.description: Welcome to 510 CR 2710, Walnut Springs! This stunning brick home is nestled on a sprawling 10-acre parcel of Texas land, creating a serene and private retreat. As you approach the property, a long private driveway with a gated entrance ensures your peace of mind and adds to the exclusivity of this residence. The landscape is adorned with magnificent large trees that provide ample shade and lend a sense of tranquility to the surroundings. As you step onto the property, you'll immediately be captivated by the charm of the home's exterior, highlighted by a spacious covered front porch that invites you to sit back, relax, and enjoy the picturesque views. Once inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room area that serves as the heart of the home. The centerpiece is a beautiful propane fireplace, which adds warmth and character to the space. The adjoining dining room seamlessly flows into the kitchen area, creating an open and inviting atmosphere perfect for entertaining guests. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed and has an abundance of counter space and cabinet storage along with a lazy Susan and pull out garbage, allowing you to unleash your culinary creativity. Whether you're preparing everyday meals or hosting lavish gatherings, this kitchen will exceed your expectations. The bedrooms in this home are all generously sized, providing ample space for relaxation and personalization. However, the main bedroom is truly exceptional, boasting grand proportions and having a private sanctuary for you to unwind. The large main bathroom features a shower tub combo and dual vanities, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routines. Convenience and functionality are seamlessly integrated into this home. The laundry room provides additional storage space and ample room for your appliances, including freezers. This ensures that your home remains organized and clutter-free. Step outside onto the covered back porch, and you'll discover a brick patio where you can savor peaceful moments in the shade of the surrounding trees. It's the perfect spot for embracing the beauty of nature that envelops this property. Grand oversized carport, pool house/ storage building, and converted garage that serves as a bonus room are more amazing additions to this home. With its charming exterior, spacious living areas, and the tranquility of the surrounding landscape, this property is a place you'll be proud to call home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the allure of this beautiful property for yourself.
